---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Ways to Give" description="When you give to the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, you're helping bring awareness, education, and support to individuals and families living with hoarding behavior.">

  <div class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Ways to Give</h1>

      <h5><mark>When you give to the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, you're helping bring awareness, education, and support to individuals and families living with hoarding behavior.</mark></h5>

      <div class="give-now-section">
        <h5><strong>Ways to Give:</strong> Online Donations<br />Online Donations are fast, easy, and convenient.</h5>
        <a href="https://givebutter.com/mnhtfgeneraldonation" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary">GIVE NOW</a>
      </div>

      <div class="giving-details">
        <div class="giving-col">
          <h5><strong>Mail-In Donations</strong></h5>
          <h5>If you prefer to mail-in donation, you can do so at the address below:<br />Minnesota Hoarding Task Force<br />P.O. Box 21483<br />Eagan, MN 55121</h5>

          <h5><strong>Events and Sponsors</strong> For upcoming events and sponsorship opportunities, contact <a href="mailto:mnhtf.org@gmail.com">mnhtf.org@gmail.com</a>.</h5>

          <h5><strong>Match Gifts</strong> Help us double our impact through Corporate Giving. Check with your Employer or Human Resources Department of more information on gift matching.</h5>

          <h5><strong>In-Kinds Gifts</strong> By volunteering your time and talent, you help us make an impact in the community, and your contributions are invaluable.</h5>

          <div class="check-image">
            <img src="/images/Handing-Over-a-Check.jpg" alt="Handing over a check" />
          </div>

          <h5><strong>Donation FAQs</strong> <strong>Local Donations</strong> When you donate to the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force, your donation maximizes impact in bringing awareness, education, and resources to those with hoarding behavior and vulnerable individuals.</h5>

          <h5><strong>Tax-Deductible</strong> Your donation is Tax-Deductible, as the Minnesota Hoarding Task Force is a 501(c)(3) organization. (EIN 81-3567154) Which means that your donation is Tax-Deductible as allowed by law.</h5>

          <h5><strong>Personal Information</strong> We respect your privacy and do not sell your email address to others. We will use it to keep you informed of MNHTF events, meetings, and information.</h5>

          <h5><mark>For additional information or questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:mnhtf.org@gmail.com">mnhtf.org@gmail.com</a>.</mark></h5>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="give-mn-badge">
        <a href="https://give.mn/fmb5wf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <img src="/images/HorizontalPrimary.png" alt="GiveMN" height="60" />
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
h5 {
  font-size: var(--font-size-base);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}
.give-now-section {
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}
.giving-details {
  margin: var(--space-6) 0;
}
.check-image {
  margin: var(--space-6) 0;
}
.check-image img {
  max-width: 400px;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}
.give-mn-badge {
  margin: var(--space-8) 0;
}
.give-mn-badge img {
  height: 60px;
  width: auto;
}
mark {
  background: transparent;
}
</style>
